{"tid":2371220,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗1月首15天錄146成交，世宙2房上劈穿新高價690萬","createTime":"2021-01-18T15:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T04:55:12.000Z","uid":73269,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"bf201dd2d44adc3c8a3ef6eaa340494124e72d0c","tid":2371220,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T15:46:16.000Z","msg":"元朗暫錄146成交  世宙2房創1年新高價690萬沽<br />\n<br />\n中原地產元朗副區域營業經理王勤學表示，二手成交暢旺，買家入市(鄉黑？)信心增強，市場不乏創新高價成交。元朗世宙3座高層J室，實用面積422平方呎，兩房間隔，景致開揚，以690萬元沽出，實用呎價16351元，造價創屋苑分層兩房單位一年新高。<br />\n<br />\n元朗區本月至今錄得146宗二手成交。大家原諒左元朗了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我未。"},{"pid":"e5c4864835d5407c3245d6f1c9da1a5c31004381","tid":2371220,"uid":357591,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"利害<br />\n<br />\n香港真係好多好多有錢人"},{"pid":"040f09211b808779b88330e178189efa127a86df","tid":2371220,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:15:20.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9b2aa88c4d73741db3676df05977fb749a0e047c","tid":2371220,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:20:06.000Z","msg":"樓借樓 剛需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022ebc1a71e223ca4e721b315944cd1af98150fc","tid":2371220,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T16:25:49.000Z","msg":"隔離仲有銀行佬唱淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n梗係啦，唱淡比佢入市丫嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a7b895ea2898bedfc03e1530d1d2523a173a13","tid":2371220,"uid":357591,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"022ebc1a71e223ca4e721b315944cd1af98150fc","tid":2